{"tid":1409410,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟諗口號","createTime":"2019-08-04T21:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T03:29:21.000Z","uid":240609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fadc59dda0f9c2ccddf36377e1574dcf5b13bc","tid":1409410,"uid":240609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:09:26.000Z","msg":"頭先開咗係吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淋奠匿係黑警後面咁耐<br />\n想撚香港人focus係仇警<br />\n除咗 光復香港 時代革命 之外<br />\n嗌返啲口號提自己 提手足<br />\n要打低嘅係淋奠政府 係中共<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></span><br />\n下一句可以點接 變做好記嘅口號<br />\n今日集會一齊嗌"},{"pid":"63cf354cda1d3275e9dbec9671f519db9079c27e","tid":1409410,"uid":240609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:09:48.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"},{"pid":"0eaef6a1b0ef0b86c138788bf086ca6dc5ec0469","tid":1409410,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:16:33.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全民三罷！<br />\n<br />\n遍地開花 九巴不合作運動最後召集！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所有最新資訊會係TG Group到發放，有意發夢參加的朋友請加入<br />\n<br />\n已有分區細group，group link係大group公怖咗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFehx0H-9ZMmNP0guA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFehx0H-9ZMmNP0guA&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=2c2d4efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFehx0H-9ZMmNP0guA</a>"},{"pid":"a6a610a544dcc50361304afe8ff94ce17a8edc42","tid":1409410,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:17:45.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳] FORWARDED FROM TELEGRAM<br />\n朋友既朋友 警隊臨床心理學家指出唔少警察<br />\n長期聽到針對警察示威口號產生幻聽、躁鬱、最嚴重會患上抑鬱等<br />\n<br />\n若示威者同警察距離非常近既時候, 利用群眾優勢<br />\n不要說「黑警，可恥」, 試著說「黑社會」,這種標籤化令警察內心會感自愧, 壓力倍僧, 行為自動檢點<br />\n<br />\n進一步造成心理創傷口號，不要說「香港警察，知法犯法」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">試著說「不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意」</span>此口號出自警察誓言, 當有人不斷叫出此口號，警察會回憶畢業既誓言，開始對自己身份認同產生懷疑同混淆, 精神疲乏, 有部份警察雙眼通紅、帶有淚光<br />\n<br />\n終極核彈級口號, 有機會造成永久心理創傷, 相信好快用得「殺人兇手」 當事實真的發生，不論兇手有沒有殺人，身處同一個群體，都變成兇手, <br />\n不單面對極大壓力而崩塌, 伴隨的是恐懼、抑鬱, 更重要是這種負面情緒會災難性地爆發傳遍整個群體"},{"pid":"cf8d40ce834f044a559fbd9429ae37d1af87fe66","tid":1409410,"uid":274180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:51:13.000Z","msg":"保衛人生安全<br />\n對準香港政權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85868a95013547f35fb3958f7ec1ec38b73a7f09","tid":1409410,"uid":40286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:51:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好比憤怒支配自己</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你地醒未啊！依家做嘅野冇撚用架！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1409458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1409458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e48a0c93fd373d7f35413edd14106be64c32fc86","tid":1409410,"uid":285344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T21:57:06.000Z","msg":"對準政權 林鄭玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0f23a0d28cf6dc210fd6bd31934324f651ce7d","tid":1409410,"uid":219153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:29:21.000Z","msg":"逃犯條例  撒回<br />\n官警黑勾結  可恥<br />\n每日百五個  取消<br />\n警方濫用武力  徹查<br />\n<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會"}]}